Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會像那時一樣改變了日本的地形
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你覺得這個首都消失了也無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才這樣做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少在你們那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有能夠阻止他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是一點時間也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心自己一不留神就將周圍燒光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以安心睡眠 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…從以前開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一直很討厭忍耐和控制這類麻煩的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真失格的王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙要是在廣闊的草原上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為獅子出生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該挺幸福的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然是這麼感性的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要做好自己分內的事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是同伴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他的興趣很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店裡的裝飾也變得很奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fad(100,1000)\blur3}八年前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 尊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最近好像被中學生纏上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那煩人的小鬼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在討厭擁有同伴 And
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諂媚傢伙的尊周圍閒晃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是大膽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您好 這裡是HOMRA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個想當你小弟的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在街上被人揍了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送到醫院去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 King
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果繼續在這傢伙身邊閒晃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會遇到這些事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你覺得在強者身邊會很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你可就想反了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在問你是被誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前 King
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能聽我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這條腿…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超癢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我撓一下腳趾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不要命的小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被殺了的話我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為王的臣下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得他會成為一個了不起的大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至會成為真正的王嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這要怎麼讀？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼讀呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你記下這個有什麼用！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我來回想一下當時寫的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟菊理聯繫一下就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要打電話？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了應付這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才會問她聯繫方式的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去問不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有必要特地回去一趟嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想電話是為什麼而存在的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾輩討厭電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊佐那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在在買煙火…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊佐那先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊佐那社
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菊理問我是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說不認識伊佐那社這人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不像開玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓的樣子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是她對菊理做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們先回學園島吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能再借我手機一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打電話給家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想別人對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「你確實是伊佐那社」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是社…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您所撥打的電話號碼是空號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請確認號碼後…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fad(800,1000)\blur3}三年前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來累積了很多壓力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚飯是冬陰功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:34.52,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,冬陰功︰泰國的海鮮酸辣湯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我睡午覺的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過是無聊的衝突罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「根本不需要KING親自解決」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草薙哥他這樣抱怨了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會成為王呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你和其他人是不一樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪個傢伙都吵著黏過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你也非常重視大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從以前開始就沒什麼責任感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可是王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量不是為了破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了守護而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保證
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冬陰功是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是酸酸辣辣的湯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然紅紅的看上去很辣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但嘗起來味道卻意外的複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安娜 一起來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正沉迷於料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給家裡打電話後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻說號碼是空號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得有幾種可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記錯了家裡電話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家裡發生了什麼事而更換了號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然就是第四種
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的記憶中有著缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是伊佐那社啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但還是有一個幸福的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是離開父母住校的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一名高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓到底去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fad(300,450)\blur3}三個月前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十束哥真是笨拙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡要嘎地過去 然後轉回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八田的說明完全聽不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滑板給我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要玩滑板到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.31,0:16:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎 十束哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}那裡要咕地往前…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}不是那邊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}後面 後面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 明明打架很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻能融入只懂打架的笨蛋們中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}沒問題啦 真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙簡直就像個馴獸師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}預備 起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你剛才笑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好遜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 不過區區八田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,排七明明笨得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十束哥才是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡玩盆栽這種老頭子的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還硬要玩滑板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡嘗試各式各樣的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前陣子我買了台挺很古老的攝影機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錄影的話 用手機不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那感覺不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用它拍了很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次給你們看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌…不唱歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安娜真是個好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被我的興趣之一所迷住的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就存在於此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太誇張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:57.70,EDJPII,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}{\a7}幾千もの交差する道で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:03.68,EDJPII,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}{\a7}僕等は出會えた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:07.16,EDJPII,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}{\a7}はしゃぎ合ったり
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:10.64,EDJPII,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}{\a7}ふざけ合ったり
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:16.62,EDJPII,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}{\a7}したあの日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:57.70,EDTCII,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}{\a7}在萬千交錯的道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:03.68,EDTCII,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}{\a7}我們相遇相惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:07.16,EDTCII,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}{\a7}曾經一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:10.64,EDTCII,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}{\a7}嬉笑遊戲的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:16.62,EDTCII,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,400)\blur3}{\a7}那些日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是你家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這裡沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從車站出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沿著街道直走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該有一棟附有小庭院的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是你自己所想的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能根本就不是伊佐那社
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有伊佐那社這個人的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我一直覺得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每當在回想一些細節的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻怎麼也想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺人犯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的可能性也不是絕對沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不能相信自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要殺了…我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fad(300,100)\blur3}一週前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十束哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十束哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到底發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無色之…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十束哥 你被其他王襲擊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 八田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 十束哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:19:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就叫醫生來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種小傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就可以治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總會有辦法的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十束哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十束哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 尊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個壞消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘是說些不負責任的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻擅自走離開我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放下心中之傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜幕不降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是絕世的名言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你聽我說話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說你不相信自己的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你變得不相信自己之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.02,0:21:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所相信的只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是故主所說的話而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一言大人說要看透一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我還沒有放棄去看透你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我還沒打算讓夜幕降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:21:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.06,0:22:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不放棄嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一言大人說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以允許你誦讀這俳句
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能誦讀一言大人偉大的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.50,0:22:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心裡也會平靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.19,0:22:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
